com.mapzen.tangram

Interface MapController.SceneLoadListener

  • Enclosing class:
    MapController

    public static interface MapController.SceneLoadListener
    Interface for listening to scene load status information. Triggered after a call of #updateSceneAsync(List) or #loadSceneFileAsync(String, List) or #loadSceneFile(String, List) Listener should be set with MapController.setSceneLoadListener(SceneLoadListener) The callbacks will be run on the main (UI) thread.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onSceneReady(int sceneId, SceneError sceneError)
      Received when a scene load or update finishes.

    • Method Detail

      • onSceneReady

        void onSceneReady(int sceneId,
                  SceneError sceneError)
        Received when a scene load or update finishes. If sceneError is not null then the operation did not succeed.
        Parameters:
        sceneId - The identifier returned by #updateSceneAsync(List) or #loadSceneFileAsync(String, List).
        sceneError - A SceneError holding error information, or null if no error occurred.
